text: The second season of I'm a Celebrity...Get Me Out of Here, which was commissioned on 16 July 2015, premiered on Network Ten on 31 January 2016. The season was won by Brendan Fevola who received $100,000 for his charity, and gave half ($50,000) to Paul Harragon's charity. == References == Category:I'm a Celebrity...Get Me Out of Here!
